方法：&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早晚洁肤后，取适量蘸湿化妆棉，顺着肌肤纹理轻柔涂于全脸，轻轻弹拍至吸收。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">玻尿酸肽粉润水肌乳 净含量：120ml</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">使用方法：&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 使用原液精华后，取适量本品涂于面颈部，轻轻按摩至吸收即可。早晚使用。</span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">玻尿酸肽保湿弹力慕丝 净含量：50g</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">使用方法：&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style="color:#999999;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;font-size:14px;line-height:normal;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 早晚清洁爽肤后，取适量均匀涂抹于面部、颈部，稍按摩至吸收；亦可做为晒后修护的面膜使用。</span>', 1471574779, 1471623155),
(2, NULL, '补水心动套组3+1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'm/store/zero_goods/20160819/05249381847031172.jpg', 'm/store/zero_goods/20160819/05249381847039356.jpg', '4444.00', '100.00', 10000, 50, 49, 0, 0, 0, 1000, 1000, 1, 1, 0, '560.00', NULL, '<h1 class="goodsname" style="font-size:32px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;vertical-align:baseline;color:#B3846B;">\r\n	<img src="http://120.25.212.243/czb/data/upload/shop/editor/20160819110010_80698.jpg" alt="" /><img src="http://120.25.212.243/czb/data/upload/shop/editor/20160819110010_63573.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</h1>\r\n<h1 class="goodsname" style="font-size:32px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;vertical-align:baseline;color:#B3846B;">\r\n	补水心动套组3+1\r\n</h1>\r\n<div style="padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 10px;border:0px;font-size:16px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;vertical-align:baseline;color:#989A97;">\r\n</div>\r\n<p class="gx" style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;vertical-align:baseline;color:#4A4A4A;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;">产品功效：</span> <a href="http://www.unescn.com/gallery--tp,7_2,0_p,0-6.html" target="_blank">补水保湿系列</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="gx" style="font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;vertical-align:baseline;color:#4A4A4A;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;">适用肤质：</span> <a href="http://www.unescn.com/gallery--tp,7_3,5_p,0-6.html" target="_blank">所有肌肤类型</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class="brief" style="font-size:14px;font-family:''Microsoft YaHei'', ''Microsoft JhengHei'', ''”Hiragino Sans GB”'', ”STHeiti”, verdana, Tahoma, arial;vertical-align:baseline;color:#999999;">\r\n	补水心动套组3+1<img src="/czb/data/upload/shop/editor/20160819105943_62074.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n温和洁面﹐优越清洁力，保持肌肤酸碱平衡，其丰富而细腻的保湿泡沫可把污垢包围﹐然后从肌肤带走﹐清洁同时特别加入保湿成分，更能滋润肌肤，给予您细腻通透照人的肌肤。提升肌肤锁水力，在对肌肤进行二次清洁和调理肌肤纹理的同时，令肌肤持续莹润光滑、水嫩有光泽。抵御外界环境对肌肤的侵袭。日复一日，肌肤被有效保护，呈现柔软细腻、水润剔透的光彩。 <br />\r\n<br />\r\n玻尿酸肽保湿洗面奶 净含量：100g <br />\r\n使用方法： <br />\r\n       早晚取适量于掌心，加少量清水或温水揉搓至产生丰富泡沫后涂于面部，轻柔打圈按摩全脸，再用水清洗干净即可。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n玻尿酸肽保湿理肤水 净含量：120ml <br />\r\n使用方法： <br />\r\n       早晚洁肤后，取适量蘸湿化妆棉，顺着肌肤纹理轻柔涂于全脸，轻轻弹拍至吸收。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n玻尿酸肽粉润水肌乳 净含量：120ml<br />\r\n使用方法： <br />\r\n       使用原液精华后，取适量本品涂于面颈部，轻轻按摩至吸收即可。早晚使用。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n玻尿酸肽保湿弹力慕丝 净含量：50g<br />\r\n使用方法： <br />\r\n       早晚清洁爽肤后，取适量均匀涂抹于面部、颈部，稍按摩至吸收；亦可做为晒后修护的面膜使用。\r\n</p>', 1471574881, 1471627509),
